    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012550/extras/17bcac2ae21e4182d2ec8fa54779d4e8.avif?t=1764084733\" width=615 height=80 /></span><br><br><strong>About</strong><br><br>The game uses George MacDonald's The Princess and the Goblin as source material. <br>Carefully selected hundreds of words has been removed from the book to let you find them. <br>And we added cats to make the audiobook more fun. <br>If you don't like reading books this might be your way in to the world of stories.<br>Even if you know the book it is still a challenge.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br>Narration: All 32 chapters of the book is fully narrated. Yes it's an audiobook but narrator does meow!<br>Music: You are welcomed with a piece from Bach.<br>Missing Words: 300+ selected words has been removed from the book.<br>Hints: For each missing word you are given a hint but not free.<br>Cats: Feed the little cats to unlock hints. (Please don't disturb the narrator while doing it)",
